com.coveros.selenified.selenium

Class Assert

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveros.selenified.selenium.Assert

  • public class Assert
extends Object
    A custom reporting class, which provides logging and screenshots for all verifications. Meant to provide additional traceability on top of TestNG Asserts
    Version:
    2.0.1
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
